values: （用于否定句、疑问句，也用于if或whether之后，或紧接prevent、forbid、avoid等动词，代替someone）任何人；无论谁；随便哪个人；某人（用于疑问句或否定句中）

sample.mean: num. 一；一个；一个人；唯一；同一个；单一；相同的；一体的；一岁；一个故事

bilingual.target: 你和任何人一起去的吗？
任何人都可以加入俱乐部。
你和任何人一起出去了吗？
你不许把这事告诉任何人。
任何人都可以成为我们的朋友！
任何人都可以参加这个工作坊。

bilingual.source: It was just something anyone can make.
bilingual.target: 它只是任何人都可以做的东西。

bilingual.source: It's not easy for anyone to say sorry.
bilingual.target: 对任何人来说，说对不起都不容易。

bilingual.source: Accidents can happen to anyone at any time.
bilingual.target: 事故随时可能发生在任何人身上。

bilingual.source: Some courses are free and open to anyone.
bilingual.target: 一些课程是免费的，向任何人开放。

list.abstract: Anyone，1999年3月9日发行的英语歌曲，歌手是Roxette，收录于专辑《Have A Nice Day》。

yingyinNormal.en: You have to swear you will not tell anyone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你必须要发誓，不会告诉任何人。

yingyinNormal.en: I promise, I never meant for anyone to get hurt.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我发誓，我没想伤害任何人。

yingyinNormal.en: It's cool coming here and being anyone I wanna be.
yingyinNormal.zh: 来这里很好成为我想成为的任何人。

yingyinNormal.en: I believe in you, Elsa. More than anyone or anything.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我信任你，艾莎，胜于任何人任何事。

yingyinNormal.en: It could be anyone, then. Any man. Yeah. Any man.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那就可能是任何人了。谁都可能是啊，谁都可能。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I know this plan better than anyone. Mr. President...
yingyinNormal.zh: 我比任何人都了解这个计划。总统先生……

yingyinNormal.en: Hagrid. Relax. I do not believe that Harry attacked anyone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 海格，不要紧张。我不相信哈利他会攻击任何人。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: He told me not to trust anyone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他让我别相信任何人。

yingyinNormal.en: I haven't told anyone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我没有告诉任何人。

yingyinNormal.en: And I didn't tell anyone or share with anyone these feelings and I just held them in and let them fester.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我没有告诉任何人，没和任何人分享我的感受，我只让它们烂在自己心里。

yingyinNormal.en: What does he know? Has he shown this to anyone? Sent it to anyone? Publishers, the press? I don't know. Well, what do you know?
yingyinNormal.zh: 他知道些什么？他给任何人看过吗？寄给过任何人吗？出版商，媒体？我不知道。那你知道什么？

yingyinNormal.en: Andrea. You do not talk to anyone. Do not look at anyone. This is of the utmost importance. You must be invisible. Do you understand?
yingyinNormal.zh: 安吉丽雅，你不能和任何人说话，不要看任何人。这是至关重要的，你必须变成隐形人，明白了吗？

yingyinNormal.en: I've never interviewed anyone before. I've actually never had anyone work for me before.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我从来没有面试过任何人，从来没有人为我工作过。

yingyinNormal.en: I haven't discussed this with anyone. I wanted to ask you first.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我没和任何人讨论过这事，我想先问你。

yingyinNormal.en: The Russians have cordoned it off. They're not letting anyone in.
yingyinNormal.zh: 俄国人已经拉起警戒线，不让任何人接近。

yingyinNormal.en: You don't say anything to Serena. You don't say anything to anyone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么都不要和瑟琳娜说，也不要和任何人说。

yingyinNormal.en: Come on, I didn't want anyone to feel bad at the end of the game.
yingyinNormal.zh: 拜托，我不想让任何人在游戏结束的时候伤心啊。

yingyinNormal.en: All right. I think you've got a secret. And it's something you won't tell anyone. Because you don't trust anyone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那好我觉得你还有个秘密，而且你不会告诉任何人，因为你谁也不信。

yingyinNormal.en: A mutant with the ability to transform herself into anyone. Mystique.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那变种人的天赋技能是可以变成任何人。魔形女。

yingyinNormal.en: How can you help them when they won't let anyone near the blast site?
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们不许任何人接近爆炸地点，你怎么能帮他们？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: After all, they may think a little dirt doesn't hurt <highlight>anyone</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 毕竟，他们可能会认为一点污垢不会伤害任何人。

examination_example.sentence: Talk to <highlight>anyone</highlight> who's a generation not too older and they would most likely comment that children are more spoiled these days.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 和任何一个年纪不大的人交谈，他们很可能会说现在的孩子更被宠坏了。

examination_example.sentence: Parents should teach children to develop their own values instead of becoming <highlight>anyone</highlight>'s shadow.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 父母应该教会孩子树立自己的价值观，而不是成为任何人的影子。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

examination_example.sentence: But can <highlight>anyone</highlight> be sure if the decline is really caused by the hunting or by climate change?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但有人能确定这种下降是真的由狩猎或是气候变化造成的吗？

examination_example.sentence: It is offering a big reward to <highlight>anyone</highlight> who helps.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它向任何提供帮助的人提供高额报酬。

examination_example.sentence: Kirsteen said: "We'll pay that to <highlight>anyone</highlight> who brings him home as long as they are not responsible for his disappearance."
examination_example.sentence_trans: 柯尔斯廷说：“只要他们不对他的失踪负责，我们会向任何把他带回家的人支付这笔钱。”

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: He offered to fix bikes free of charge for <highlight>anyone</highlight> who needed it.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他为任何需要的人免费修理自行车。

examination_example.sentence: If <highlight>anyone</highlight> had told me three years ago that I would be spending most of my weekends camping.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果三年前有人告诉我的话，我会把大部分周末都花在露营上。

examination_example.sentence: He would laugh the loudest over fun and be the saddest over <highlight>anyone</highlight>'s misfortune.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 遇到有趣的事他笑得最为爽朗，当别人不幸时他会伤心断肠。
